## Task

Write a brief one-to-two sentence summary of the supplied documents (visible
as `<document>` context messages above) into `body.text` and set
`main_topic` to the shared topic across them.

## Required citations

You MUST populate `body.citations` with a tuple of one or more
`DocumentCitation` objects. Each citation MUST set `document_id` equal to
the `<id>` of one of the supplied documents (the IDs appear inside the
`<document>` XML envelope of each context message). Citations without a
`document_id` will be rejected by the contract.

## Format

Set `body.citations` to a list of objects shaped like:

```
{"document_id": "<copied-id-from-context>"}
```

Use at least one citation. Copy the document_id verbatim from the
`<id>...</id>` element in the supplied context.
